  - `EndPerformanceMeasurement()`: End measurement and update display
  - `UpdatePerformanceDisplay()`: Refresh metrics label (thread-safe)
- **Integration Points**: All 17 button click handlers wrapped with measurement calls
- **Display Control**: `lblPerformanceMetrics` on right side of window
