## Testing Recommendations

### Baseline Testing
1. Run each algorithm in FAST mode 3 times ? Average the times
2. Store these as baselines
3. Use for regression detection after code changes

### Slow vs Fast Comparison
1. Run algorithm in FAST mode ? Note time
2. Run same algorithm in SLOW mode ? Watch and note time
3. Review ratio: Algorithms with 5x+ ratios have visible steps

### Stress Testing
1. Run all 17 algorithms in rapid succession
2. Check that memory doesn't accumulate (should stay <5 MB)
3. Verify label updates correctly for each algorithm
4. Confirm no UI freezes or delays

### Performance Counter Testing
1. On different Windows versions/configurations
2. Verify graceful degradation if counters unavailable
3. Test on systems with CPU restrictions/virtualization

